snippet.textDisplay:
I do not wanna be rude... However, I love this Lilabali song since my childhood. I played this song last year, in my brother's gaye holud. When I saw this song on Cokestudio bangla. I became sooo excited but the song couldn't impress me, even a bit. 
I love this song, I am a fan of Arnob's song... I couldn't just leave the song mid way. I listened the whole song with the hope of liking this remake piece. But what happened, how can this be sooo bad??!!!!! It just doesn't follow the formula!!!! The song was sooo fast paced, I actually felt ,may be my play speed was increased... so ,I checked my settings, it was on right place speed... but I was soo desperate to like this song, I even tried this song by decreasing the play speed but it didn't really fit with background music. I am super disappointed. And I had to express... It's Lilabali and it's Arnob...my two favorites....
